These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, azalea, sunflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, engineer, journalist, chef
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, aquamarine, black, yellow
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, electronic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, vegafina, dunhill, baccarat
 1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the engineer is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the chef is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the fan of classical is the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the electrician##1
 9. the person who likes black is the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is the person who likes aquamarine##1
11. the electrician is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower          | zinnia    | azalea      | daisy  | sunflower     |
| Job         | chef    | journalist   | electrician | engineer      |
| Color   | aquamarine       | azure | black     | yellow    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | d&b         | classical  | dubstep    |
| Cigar           | dunhill      | baccarat       | bongani | vegafina |

