.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, yellow, blood-red, lavender
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, sudoku, fishing, magic-tricks
City: edinburgh, rome, hannover, san-francisco
There are 4 different nationalities: american, italian, malaysian, russian
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the american##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the italian##1
 3. the russian is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 6. the malaysian is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Color      | yellow      | coral     | blood-red    | lavender |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Hobby   | sudoku  | magic-tricks     | fishing    | rock-climbing         |
| City           | san-francisco         | rome | hannover     | edinburgh        |
| Nationality         | american     | russian  | italian | malaysian       |

