.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, analyst, teacher, musician
City: rome, liverpool, berlin, san-francisco
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, soul, d&b
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, reading, magic-tricks, board-games
 1. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the teacher is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the analyst is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the right of the musician##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the teacher##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the teacher is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Job          | nurse    | musician      | teacher  | analyst   |
| City   | san-francisco     | berlin      | liverpool | rome      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Music-Genre         | gospel | hip-hop | soul  | d&b |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks       | dancing         | board-games   | reading        |

