4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dannemann, havana, game
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, taxi, trike
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 4. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| City      | rome   | miami   | prague      | hannover     |
| Movie-Genre          | superhero     | disaster   | animation | scientific |
