.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, july, january
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, balloon-flower, lily
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, disaster, mystery
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, domino, bridge
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person playing canasta##1
10. the person drinking water is the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| Birthday       | july    | january        | december  | february      |
| Flower         | rose  | lily | daffodil | balloon-flower |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | mystery          | time-travel         | disaster      |
| Game   | canasta     | mah-jongg     | domino       | bridge          |

