.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, country, pop, electronic
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, journalist, musician, scientist
There 4 different types of food: cherry, apricot, mango, peas
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, ship, train, car
 1. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of country is the scientist##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of pop##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the journalist##1
 8. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the ship is the musician##1
10. the musician is on the far left##1
11. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of country##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre      | electronic       | pop      | country      | rock    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | video-games | magic-tricks | dancing  |
| Job   | musician    | journalist     | scientist      | bartender |
| Food   | mango  | peas     | cherry    | apricot  |
| Transport           | ship  | car       | jet-ski          | train      |

