.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, cola, juice
4 different games are played: go, domino, poker, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, turquise, pink, red
House: wooden, gothic-revival, ranch-style, craftsman
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, ship
 1. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person playing go##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person playing poker##1
 4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the craftsman house is the person drinking cola##1
11. the wooden house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
13. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage          | juice      | fanta     | coffee        | cola     |
| Game         | poker     | go    | scrabble | domino |
| Color   | ivory | pink  | turquise      | red       |
| House         | ranch-style      | wooden | gothic-revival     | craftsman        |
| Transport     | motorbike   | ship     | helicopter  | jet-ski       |

