.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, montecristo, dunhill, pall-mall
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, daffodil, bellflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, coral, azure, purple
City: marseilles, venice, liverpool, miami
 1. the person who growsbellflower is the aristoff-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who likes azure is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
10. the person eating grapes is the person who likes purple##1
11. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
12. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Cigar       | dunhill       | aristoff       | montecristo      | pall-mall |
| Flower         | lily | bellflower | daffodil | poppy      |
| Color         | ivory          | purple         | coral           | azure    |
| City   | liverpool         | venice       | miami     | marseilles   |

 